      <title>中国研究实施央行债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/china-studying-implementation-of-pboc-bond-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行行长潘功胜表示，央行正在与财政部研究如何实施国债交易。但他否认这种做法等同于量化宽松。彭博电视台记者刘敏敏报道。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-19/china-studying-implementation-of-pboc-bond-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:46:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称中国可能在七中全会前全面改革消费税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/china-may-overhaul-consumer-taxes-as-plenum-looms-goldman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团称，中国执政党共产党下个月将召开一次重要会议，该会议通常将为长期经济政策制定方向，中国可能正在考虑改革消费税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/china-may-overhaul-consumer-taxes-as-plenum-looms-goldman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:40:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
