      <title>捷豹路虎将恢复 Freelander 的中国产电动车版</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/jaguar-land-rover-to-revive-freelander-as-a-made-in-china-ev</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在停止生产神行者 (Freelander) 十年后，捷豹路虎汽车有限公司 (Jaguar Land Rover Automotive Plc) 重新推出了这款四轮驱动汽车，并将其作为电动汽车在中国生产和销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/jaguar-land-rover-to-revive-freelander-as-a-made-in-china-ev</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行再次提出限制 140 亿美元现金刺激计划的提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/thai-central-bank-renews-case-to-limit-14-billion-cash-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行仍然坚决反对政府向几乎所有成年公民发放近 140 亿美元现金以重振消费活动的计划，并表示谨慎的做法是限制对有需要的人的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/thai-central-bank-renews-case-to-limit-14-billion-cash-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
